664
00:55:47,135 --> 00:55:49,137
That's just the nature of elections.

665
00:55:49,721 --> 00:55:50,555
Fine.

666
00:55:52,599 --> 00:55:54,476
I like your self-confidence,

667
00:55:55,977 --> 00:55:58,480
but from now on,
I'd like you to be more modest

668
00:55:59,814 --> 00:56:02,025
and more meticulous in your support of me.

669
