Oh Kyung-sook's reputation for integrity.

670
00:56:09,949 --> 00:56:13,578
Integrity is the most valuable virtue
of any candidate.

671
00:56:15,163 --> 00:56:15,997
Is that why…

672
00:56:17,999 --> 00:56:19,918
you didn't tell me about Han I-seul?

