because you messed with her?

678
00:56:41,689 --> 00:56:43,274
You want to get into politics,

679
00:56:43,358 --> 00:56:45,902
but couldn't even keep
some little chick in check?

680
00:56:46,403 --> 00:56:47,445
On top of that,

681
00:56:48,488 --> 00:56:51,491
you don't even know exactly
how much Hwang Do-hee knows about that.

682
00:56:51,574 --> 00:56:54,661
