to evaluate my performance?

683
00:56:55,537 --> 00:56:58,123
That is no way to treat
a precious helper like me

684
00:56:58,832 --> 00:57:00,333
who entered this race for you.

685
00:57:00,834 --> 00:57:03,086
I'll dig further into Hwang Do-hee.

686
00:57:03,169 --> 00:57:05,046
You should focus on Oh Kyung-sook.

687
00:57:05,630 --> 00:57:07,048
An election is never over…

688
00:57:07,132 --> 00:57:08,383
…until it's over.

689
00:57:10,218 --> 00:57:13,888
From now, we'll be on the offensive,
ignoring all strategies and planning.

690
00:57:15,223 --> 00:57:17,600
Taking down Baek Jae-min
will be our only concern.

691
00:57:17,684 --> 00:57:20,520
Ms. Hwang, where should we start?

692
00:57:21,146 --> 00:57:22,439
People's emotions.

693
00:57:22,522 --> 00:57:25,150
We'll shake up the emotions
of Baek Jae-min's supporters.

694
00:57:25,733 --> 00:57:29,654
