using Aunt Hwa-soo?

695
00:57:29,737 --> 00:57:31,406
-Just like that?
-What?

696
00:57:32,532 --> 00:57:35,660
Was Baek Jae-min behind Aunt Hwa-soo?
Not the People's Servant?

697
00:57:36,578 --> 00:57:39,456
Seo Min-jung received the ball
from Baek Jae-min.

698
00:57:39,539 --> 00:57:42,667
To anger the female voters,
our key supporters.

699
00:57:42,750 --> 00:57:45,295
We'll direct it
at the Korean Republican Party.

700
00:57:46,254 --> 00:57:48,089
Until women's fury

701
00:57:49,340 --> 00:57:50,884
turns into vengeance

702
00:57:52,844 --> 00:57:54,679
and shows Baek Jae-min hell.

703
00:58:09,277 --> 00:58:11,863
Admit what?

704
00:58:12,906 --> 00:58:14,908
Admit

705
00:58:15,867 --> 00:58:17,035
what you did to me.

706
00:58:19,329 --> 00:58:20,330
Ms. Han I-seul.

707
00:58:21,456 --> 00:58:22,832
What are you talking about?

708
00:58:24,083 --> 00:58:26,336
Ms. Hwang told me to resign.

709
00:58:28,004 --> 00:58:30,882
I'm so angry and frustrated,
but there's nothing I can do.

710
00:58:31,716 --> 00:58:34,802
Should I at least get my severance pay,
or should I just kill myself?

711
00:58:35,386 --> 00:58:39,307
I've had so many thoughts cross my mind,
but this just isn't right.

712
00:58:39,390 --> 00:58:40,266
And?

713
00:58:41,142 --> 00:58:42,060
The wrongdoer…

714
00:58:44,312 --> 00:58:46,231
should pay for what they did.

715
00:58:49,943 --> 00:58:50,777
Yes.

716
00:58:52,070 --> 00:58:53,154
You're right, I-seul.

717
00:58:55,740 --> 00:58:58,451
I admit that I made you feel bad.

718
00:58:59,702 --> 00:59:00,537
