726
00:59:27,730 --> 00:59:29,691
I'll do as you say.

727
00:59:35,530 --> 00:59:36,906
But on one condition.

728
00:59:38,866 --> 00:59:39,951
Tell the world

729
00:59:41,327 --> 00:59:43,079
what you did

730
00:59:44,330 --> 00:59:46,207
and publicly apologize to me.

731
00:59:48,710 --> 00:59:50,003
Then I'll forgive you.

732
00:59:50,086 --> 00:59:52,463
-Hey, Han I-seul--
-Don't you dare say my name!

733
00:59:54,799 --> 00:59:56,384
Not until I forgive you.

