So, what?

784
01:06:22,603 --> 01:06:24,522
If you could buy a home,

785
01:06:25,189 --> 01:06:27,316
would you gladly shake hands with Satan?

786
01:06:27,900 --> 01:06:31,612
We must not fall for the sweet lies
that come from the devil's black tongue.

787
01:06:31,696 --> 01:06:32,530
You're right.

788
01:06:33,406 --> 01:06:36,534
You are all being lied to.

789
01:06:37,118 --> 01:06:40,913
Because they can't do it,
they put a halt to redevelopment

790
01:06:40,997 --> 01:06:43,582
and put forth regulations
by telling you they're unfair.

791
01:06:43,666 --> 01:06:45,793
I, Baek Jae-min, promise you this.

792
01:06:45,876 --> 01:06:47,253
The Eunsung Group's safe!

793
01:06:48,379 --> 01:06:49,463
I will open it.

794
01:06:49,547 --> 01:06:50,881
It's not a safe.

795
01:06:50,965 --> 01:06:53,050
It's your gateway to hell.

796
01:06:53,134 --> 01:06:56,220
They're leading you into the sewers
using wealth as bait.

797
01:06:56,303 --> 01:07:00,766
You must not let them deceive you
into the gates of hell, the sewers!

798
01:07:00,850 --> 01:07:02,810
Justice? What is your plan to achieve it?

799
01:07:02,893 --> 01:07:05,354
Are unrealistic ideals like justice
more important

800
01:07:05,438 --> 01:07:09,817
than the dreams of ordinary folks
who only wish to become homeowners?

801
01:07:09,900 --> 01:07:11,152
Dear citizens.

802
01:07:11,235 --> 01:07:13,696
Seoul is still bursting
with lands of opportunity.

803
01:07:14,321 --> 01:07:17,616
And I, Baek Jae-min, will make
those opportunities a reality for you!

804
01:07:17,700 --> 01:07:19,869
SOONJUNG DISTRICT REDEVELOPMENT CONFIRMED

805
01:07:19,952 --> 01:07:21,787
It's utter nonsense!
They say words can kill!

806
01:07:21,871 --> 01:07:23,330
The dream to own your own homes…

807
01:07:23,414 --> 01:07:24,999
…the wholesome dream of Seoul citizens

808
01:07:25,082 --> 01:07:25,916
I will

809
01:07:26,459 --> 01:07:27,752
make that dream come true!

810
01:07:27,835 --> 01:07:30,046
He is using it
for his political aspirations!

811
01:07:30,129 --> 01:07:32,548
A rich homeowner in Seoul!

812
01:07:33,049 --> 01:07:34,592
I'll make that dream come true!

813
01:07:34,675 --> 01:07:36,677
Do not let yourself be deceived.

814
01:07:36,761 --> 01:07:39,096
Do not be tempted by lies.

815
01:07:39,180 --> 01:07:42,349
I look forward to the wise decisions
of the citizens of Seoul.

816
01:07:42,433 --> 01:07:46,479
Politics for the common people!
I, Oh Kyung-sook, will make it happen.

817
01:07:49,231 --> 01:07:51,942
-Baek Jae-min!
-Baek Jae-min!

818
01:07:53,069 --> 01:07:54,862
You fucking bastard! I'll kill you!

819
01:07:54,945 --> 01:07:56,655
Let go of me!

820
01:08:02,787 --> 01:08:07,666
-Oh Kyung-sook!
-Oh Kyung-sook!

821
01:08:07,750 --> 01:08:11,128
-Oh Kyung-sook!
-Oh Kyung-sook!

822
01:10:04,658 --> 01:10:08,037
ALL CHARACTERS, ORGANIZATIONS, LOCATIONS,
INSTITUTIONS, AND EVENTS

823
01:10:08,120 --> 01:10:09,747
IN THIS DRAMA ARE FICTITIOUS

